Feature: Projects

  Core functionality for interacting with projects

  Scenario: When a user is created they don not have any projects

  Scenario: There should be a proposition to newly created user to create project

  Scenario: A user has a project if he is a member of it

  Scenario: After creating a project, the user becomes its member with the root role

  Scenario: A user can be a member of projects in the number from 0 to infinity
